#. Tag: title
#: introduction.docbook:7
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "介绍"

#. Tag: title
#: introduction.docbook:9
#, no-c-format
msgid "What is &kmymoney;?"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: introduction.docbook:10
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmymoney; is a personal finance manager by &kde;. It enables users to keep "
"careful track of their personal finances by providing a broad array of "
"financial features and tools."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: introduction.docbook:16
#, no-c-format
msgid "The principal goals of the project are:"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: introduction.docbook:22
#, no-c-format
msgid "Feature Parity"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: introduction.docbook:23
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmymoney; intends to provide all important features found in the "
"commercially available personal finance managers. Although every release of "
"&kmymoney; gets closer and closer to that goal, there is still work to be "
"done."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: introduction.docbook:33
#, no-c-format
msgid "Ease of Use"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: introduction.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmymoney; strives to be the easiest open source personal finance manager to "
"use, especially for the non-technical user."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: introduction.docbook:42
#, no-c-format
msgid "Correctness"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: introduction.docbook:43
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Based on tried and tested double entry accounting principles, &kmymoney; "
"ensures that your finances are kept in correct order."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: introduction.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
msgid "What &kmymoney; is not"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: introduction.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As a personal finance manager, &kmymoney; is not intended to support the "
"needs of a business. A small business might find sufficient functionality to "
"use &kmymoney;, but features such as accounts-receivable and accounts-"
"payable are not directly supported. The larger the business, the less likely "
"it is to find &kmymoney; will meet its financial management needs. Most if "
"not all the data needed for a small business, such as for reports for audit "
"and taxation purposes is present, but may need to be extracted using various "
"reports and then processed and assembled into the required formats. In "
"addition, it would be possible to create client, supplier, document, or "
"other features through plugins."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: introduction.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmymoney; is not simply a clone of any of the commercially available "
"personal finance programs. Although many of the features present in "
"&kmymoney; can be found in other similar applications, &kmymoney; strives to "
"present an individual and unique view of your finances."
msgstr ""
